{"tid":203080,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"新手養貓 求救","createTime":"2017-04-16T04:35:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T06:16:59.000Z","uid":13559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10bf42ec68097ab61f23b67303ca4ade522d4df8","tid":203080,"uid":13559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:35:26.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我同男朋友黎緊月尾準備養兩隻近兩個月大既bb貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想問一問大家<br />\n1. 除左貓窩砂盆同貓糧，仲有咩可以準備得好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2. 打針果邊 想問可以去邊度打會安全啲同平啲<br />\n3. 想問啲臨時貓窗網可以係邊度買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n準備做奴才 真係好開心又緊張<br />\n其後 一定 奉上主子既圖俾各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ed3e40957440ea26fc03ded2df540c828b079c","tid":203080,"uid":51238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T05:50:00.000Z","msg":"窗網<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22783dd5b0fafba1010ad5c11a1812a07285d6c5","tid":203080,"uid":13559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T07:23:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>窗網<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係邊度買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57b50ffb99b8b466eebfa0d4483cd73badcae61","tid":203080,"uid":51238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T07:26:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>窗網<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係邊度買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.catsocietyhk.org/cat-knowledge/window-safety/?mobile=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.catsocietyhk.org%2Fcat-knowledge%2Fwindow-safety%2F%3Fmobile%3D1&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=415a9ede\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.catsocietyhk.org/cat-knowledge/window-safety/?mobile=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03169e77e37daef4fad40292cff1a6a331d717e4","tid":203080,"uid":61359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T07:28:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>窗網<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係邊度買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>窗網<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係邊度買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平就吉之島12蚊店買格仔網,加索帶綁係窗花,唔岩SIZE可以用老虎鉗自己剪<br />\n貴就整新窗花,不過2個月大要整得好密先得<br />\n<br />\n仲要貓籠,貓抓板,指甲鉗,梳,杜蟲杜蚤藥(未杜既話),再多少少就準備埋幾條毛巾/濕紙巾/尿片(e.g放係梳化嗱)"},{"pid":"0f99b0d82f41ba182fe30c9303d92db141d7e794","tid":203080,"uid":13559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T08:20:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>窗網<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係邊度買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.catsocietyhk.org/cat-knowledge/window-safety/?mobile=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.catsocietyhk.org%2Fcat-knowledge%2Fwindow-safety%2F%3Fmobile%3D1&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=415a9ede\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.catsocietyhk.org/cat-knowledge/window-safety/?mobile=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打"},{"pid":"b0fa05ca9d5ba531fd8e3bcd3de6ce513533634c","tid":203080,"uid":13559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T08:21:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>窗網<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係邊度買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>窗網<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係邊度買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平就吉之島12蚊店買格仔網,加索帶綁係窗花,唔岩SIZE可以用老虎鉗自己剪<br />\n貴就整新窗花,不過2個月大要整得好密先得<br />\n<br />\n仲要貓籠,貓抓板,指甲鉗,梳,杜蟲杜蚤藥(未杜既話),再多少少就準備埋幾條毛巾/濕紙巾/尿片(e.g放係梳化嗱)</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n真係冇諗過梳化嗱都會痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31a9f0f14dde9a6c73f33590661a12882ce044a","tid":203080,"uid":12259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T06:16:59.000Z","msg":"杜蟲杜蚤藥 有咩好推介"}]}